metadata.name: Glimpse of US
metadata.description:
𝔊𝔩𝔦𝔪𝔭𝔰𝔢 𝔬𝔣 𝔘𝔖

Look around. Many a time, your understanding of every 'Mona Lisa' is simply a result of how it is poised at you - a concrete viewpoint is always far off.  Just like every 'Mona Lisa' out there, we are all moving figures who inadvertently let outsiders see bit by bit of us every now and then. It never comes fully at first. 

Take your time with this piece and reflect on it.  
————  
Photo VOGUE published "Glimpse of US" under Layo Agbaje's portfolio.
